These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, german, indonesian, colombian, turkish, canadian, australian
1. the german is in the middle##1
2. the german is on the left of the indonesian##1
3. the turkish is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the indian is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the australian is on the far left##1
6. the canadian is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | australian | colombian | turkish | german | indonesian | indian | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  fisherman, police-officer, paramedic, chef, dancer, engineer, bartender
1. the bartender is on the far right##1
2. the fisherman is on the far left##1
3. the fisherman is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the dancer is on the left of the paramedic##1
5. the chef is on the right of the engineer##1
6. the bartender is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | fisherman | dancer | paramedic | engineer | chef | police-officer | bartender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: chess, cooking, writing, reading, photography, singing, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | photography | chess | singing | writing | puzzles | cooking | reading |

 #################################

 
