2. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | family | comedy | adventure | animation | romance | superhero |

